<br>
start session 1 get to server select screen<br>
window key (w2k) alt+shift+r (xp)<br>
start session 2 get to account details<br>
switch to session 1<br>
select fv click play<br>
wait til your at char spinny screen<br>
switch to session 2<br>
finish loading to spinny screen (notice it takes longer)<br>
switch to session 1<br>
enter world<br>
soo as your in eq world switch session 2 and enter world<br>
<br>
thats it <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
